  "accident_info_html": "<div><h3 class=\"tit\">사건ㆍ사고의 유형</h3>\r\nㅇ 경범죄(주거침입, 절도, 강도폭행 등)<br><br>\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"tit\">자연재해</h3>\r\nㅇ 사이클론(Cyclone) 11월~4월<br></div>",
  "local_contact_html": "<div>\n<h3 class=\"tit\">대사관 연락처</h3>\n<p>※ 쿡제도에는 우리 대사관이 없으며, 주뉴질랜드한국대사관이 겸임하고 있습니다.<br>\n<span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ 주소 :&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">Level 20, ANZ Centre, 171 Featherston Street, Wellington 6011, New Zealand</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: -0.4px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ 이메일 :&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- 일반문의 :&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:info-nz@mofa.go.kr\">info-nz@mofa.go.kr</a></p>\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- 영사&nbsp;및 비자&nbsp;:&nbsp;consular-nz@mofa.go.kr, consular2-nz@mofa.go.kr</p>\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- 정무 :&nbsp;sebyuk.yang@mofa.go.kr</p>\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- 경제 :&nbsp;economic-nz@mofa.go.kr</p>\n<p style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- 문화홍보 :&nbsp;jhkim69@mofa.go.kr<br>\nㅇ 대표번호(근무시간 중) : (64) 4-473-9073<br></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ 긴급연락처(사건사고 등 긴급상황 발생 시, 24시간) : (64) 21-0269-3271</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: -0.4px;\"></p>\n<h3 class=\"tit\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; background-image: url(&quot;../../images/front/br_02.svg&quot;); letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">현지 긴급 연락처</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">&nbsp;</span>경찰&middot;화재&middot;응급 : +682-999&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.025em;\">경</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.025em;\">찰 본부 : +682-22-499</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.025em;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<h3 class=\"tit\">주재국 신고</h3>\n<p>ㅇ 경찰 : 929</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ&nbsp;</span>화재 : 996</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ&nbsp;</span>응급&nbsp;: 998<br></p>\n<h3 class=\"tit\">의료기관 연락처</h3>\n<p>ㅇ Rarotonga Hospital : (682) 20-068</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Noto Sans KR'; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: -0.4px;\">ㅇ Medical Emergency : (</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.025em;\">682)-999</span></p></div><grammarly-desktop-integration data-grammarly-shadow-root=\"true\"></grammarly-desktop-integration>",
